This build of Nitrogen has been tested on:

Operating Systems:
  - Mac OSX Leopard with Erlang R12B-5


HTTP Platforms:
  - Inets included with Erlang R12B-5
  - Yaws 1.77
  - Mochiweb as of March 7th, 2009

---

This build of Nitrogen uses the following embedded technology:

Javascript Libraries:
  - JQuery 1.3.2
  - JQuery UI 1.7
  - Live Validation 1.3

---

Feel free to modify this document as appropriate.
If you find any issues, file them at http://nitrogen.lighthouseapp.com